TABLE.name: Photometric Data for NGC 1068
TABLE.DESCRIPTION: Published and Homogenized by NED [Frequency, Flux Density] Units

FIELD.name: DataPointNumber
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: A sequential number of Photometry Measurement for this object, applicable to this list only.

FIELD.name: DataSpectralPassBand
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Colloquial descriptions of the frequency or wavelength at which the data were collected, identifying the bandpass by name e.g., "V","1.4GHz", "6 cm", "HI", etc.

FIELD.name: DataFluxPublishedValue
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: The published photometry or fluxes for this point.

FIELD.name: DataFluxPublishedStatErr
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: The published uncertainty for photometric data.

FIELD.name: DataFluxPublishedUnit
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Units of photometry measurement for this point.

FIELD.name: DataFluxValue
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Flux/Photometric data for this point as transformed and stored by NED.

FIELD.name: DataFluxStatErr
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Symmetric Photometric/Flux uncertainty as transformed and stored by NED.

FIELD.name: DataFluxUnit
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Absolute units of photometry measurement for this point.

FIELD.name: DataSignificance
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Type of uncertainty reported in the original publication

FIELD.name: DataSpectralPublishedValue
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Wavelength or frequency of observation as given in the original publication.

FIELD.name: DataFrequencyMode
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: The method(s) by which the data were collected, reduced, or derived, regarding the frequency or wavelength.

FIELD.name: DataTargetPos
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: The position at which the measurements were taken, followed by the coordinate reference frame (e.g., 013350.90 +303935.8 (J2000) in format HHMMSS.ss +DDMMSS.s (EQUINOX), etc.).

FIELD.name: DataSpatialMode
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: The method(s) by which the data were collected, reduced, or derived, regarding the spatially integrated flux.

FIELD.name: DataQualifiers
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Self-explanatory notes pertaining to the history of the data or adjustments to the data or hanges introduced by NED.

FIELD.name: DataComments
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Other information from the published source or from NED that may be helpful in interpreting or qualifying the data.

PARAM.name: Title
PARAM.value: Photometric Data for NGC 1068, calculated by NED from available published values

PARAM.name: SpectralAxisCoverageLocation
PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Spectral coord value, NED is providing that for each point, for the collection it is not applicable.

PARAM.name: SpectralAxisCoverageBoundsExtent
PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Width of spectrum, NED is not providing that for the collection

PARAM.name: SpectralAxisCoverageBoundsStart
PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Start in spectral coord, NED is providing many single points, so no value for this param

PARAM.name: SpectralAxisCoverageBoundsStop
PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Stop in spectral coord, NED is providing many single points, so no value for this param

PARAM.name: TimeAxisCoverageLocation
PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Exposure midpoint, NED is providing many single points, so no value for this param

PARAM.name: TimeAxisCoverageBoundsExtent
PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Total elapsed time, NED is providing many single points, each could have its exposure time, so no value for this param
